{"id": "art-65", "label": "Art. 65", "title": "Art. 65: Conţinutul şi modul de executare a pedepsei accesorii a interzicerii exercitării unor drepturi", "slug": "art-65", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 65: Con&#355;inutul &#351;i modul de executare a pedepsei accesorii\na interzicerii exercit&#259;rii unor drepturi </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1678680368\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1445\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1678680368\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Pedeapsa accesorie const&#259; în interzicerea\nexercit&#259;rii drepturilor prev&#259;zute la art. 66 alin. (1) lit. a), b)\n&#351;i d)-o), a c&#259;ror exercitare a fost interzis&#259; de\ninstan&#355;&#259; ca pedeaps&#259; complementar&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1495633583\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1444\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1495633583\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259;, pedeapsa\naccesorie const&#259; în interzicerea de c&#259;tre instan&#355;&#259; a\nexercit&#259;rii drepturilor prev&#259;zute la art. 66 alin. (1) lit. a)-o) sau\na unora dintre acestea.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1739812279\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1443\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1739812279\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pedeapsa\naccesorie a interzicerii exercit&#259;rii unor drepturi se execut&#259; din\nmomentul r&#259;mânerii definitive a hot&#259;rârii de condamnare &#351;i\npân&#259; când pedeapsa principal&#259; privativ&#259; de libertate a fost\nexecutat&#259; sau considerat&#259; ca executat&#259;.</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) ICCJ admite recursul în interesul\nlegii formulat de procurorul general al Parchetului de pe lâng&#259; Înalta\nCurte de Casa&#355;ie &#351;i Justi&#355;ie &#351;i, în consecin&#355;&#259;:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>În interpretarea &#351;i aplicarea\nunitar&#259; a dispozi&#355;iilor art. 65 alin. (3) din Codul penal,\nstabile&#351;te c&#259;: aplicarea pedepselor accesorii constând în\ninterzicerea drepturilor prev&#259;zute de art. 66 alin. (1) lit. a), b)\n&#351;i d)-o) din Codul penal, a c&#259;ror exercitare a fost interzis&#259; de\ninstan&#355;&#259; ca pedeaps&#259; complementar&#259;, nu este posibil&#259;\nîn cazul dispunerii unei solu&#355;ii de condamnare la pedeapsa amenzii.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1946094429\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1442\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1946094429\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259;, pedeapsa\naccesorie având con&#355;inutul prev&#259;zut la art. 66 alin. (1) lit. c) se\npune în executare la data liber&#259;rii condi&#355;ionate sau dup&#259; ce\npedeapsa a fost considerat&#259; ca executat&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 2:Pedepsele complementare</span></b></p>"}